# Google Maps API Key (optional)
# Enable precise street-level geocoding to fix same-town location collapsing.
#
# How to get it:
# 1. Create a Google Cloud project: https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Enable: Maps JavaScript API, Geocoding API
# 3. Create an API key: APIs & Services → Credentials
# 4. Restrict it by HTTP referrer (IMPORTANT):
#    - Application restrictions → HTTP referrers
#    - Add: https://your-vercel-domain.vercel.app/*
#    - Add: http://localhost:*
# 5. Copy the key below
#
# Leave blank to use offline coordinates (town/postal level).
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# Auth Redirect URLs (update with your actual domain)
# Local: http://localhost:5173
# Production: https://your-domain.com (set in Supabase console)
